StartFrame - Class in Views
A StartFrame is an extended version of JFrame that shown while the MainFrame is creating.
StartFrame() - Constructor for class Views.StartFrame
Starts a parallel thread, where MainFrame is being created, creates visible StartFrame object and runs 60 seconds timer, which closes the StartFrame if no button was pressed.
